<page>
	
	<topic>json_standardize()</topic>
	<description>JSON_standardize() function - Takes non-standard JSON and standardizes it. Also corrects for trailing commas in the JSON (which are illegal)
</description>
	
	<syntax>json_standardize(c json [,l flagreformat ])</syntax>
	
	

	<example><![CDATA[?json_standardize("{name: 'Fred', age: 21}")
 {
"name": "Fred",
"age": 21
}

?json_standardize("{name: 'Fred', age: 21,}")
 {
"name": "Fred",
"age": 21
}]]></example>

